### Moderation API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Variables
@moderationItemId = 1

### 1. Report Content (Public Endpoint)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content_type": "service",
  "content_id": 123,
  "reason": "Spam or misleading",
  "details": "This service description contains false information"
}

### 2. Get Moderation Queue (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/queue?page=1&limit=20&status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Moderation Queue with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/queue?page=1&limit=20&status=pending&content_type=service&priority=high
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Moderation Item by ID (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/{{moderationItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Review Moderation Item - Approve (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/{{moderationItemId}}/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "approve",
  "reason": "Content complies with community guidelines",
  "admin_notes": "Reviewed and approved"
}

### 6. Review Moderation Item - Reject (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/{{moderationItemId}}/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "reject",
  "reason": "Content violates community guidelines",
  "admin_notes": "Contains inappropriate content"
}

### 7. Review Moderation Item - Flag (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/{{moderationItemId}}/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "flag",
  "reason": "Needs further review",
  "admin_notes": "Flagged for supervisor review"
}

### 8. Bulk Moderation Actions - Approve (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "moderation_item_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "action": "approve",
  "reason": "Bulk approval of verified content",
  "admin_notes": "Bulk reviewed and approved"
}

### 9. Bulk Moderation Actions - Reject (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "moderation_item_ids": [4, 5, 6],
  "action": "reject",
  "reason": "Bulk rejection of inappropriate content",
  "admin_notes": "Bulk reviewed and rejected"
}

### 10. Get Moderation History (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/history?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Moderation History with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/history?page=1&limit=20&status=approved&content_type=service
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Get Moderation Actions for Item (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/moderation/admin/{{moderationItemId}}/actions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Report Review Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content_type": "review",
  "content_id": 456,
  "reason": "Inappropriate language",
  "details": "Review contains offensive language"
}

### 14. Report Message Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content_type": "message",
  "content_id": 789,
  "reason": "Harassment",
  "details": "Message contains harassing content"
}

### 15. Report Profile Content
POST {{baseUrl}}/moderation/reports
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "content_type": "profile",
  "content_id": 321,
  "reason": "Fake profile",
  "details": "Profile appears to be fake or impersonating"
}

